entry.title: about
entry.content: Hey, my name is Lachlan. I’m a first year undergraduate student at the University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign pursuing a degree in physics with minors in computer science and math. I’m very interested in scientific computing and simulating real-world phenomena using code.
